<p>The renovations are finished! This generator is almost entirely JavaScript. <b>Known issues:</b><br>
- A bunch of location words (like <i>sallonu</i>) are mistakenly set to be indirect objects of some verbs (i.e "She is hitting on behalf of the shoreline"). This is not supposed to be the case. Please tell me if you see one of these words being the indirect object like that.<br>
- Adjectives and the genitive marker can now be used and I'm worried they're going to break or do something stupid. Let me know if something breaks or if a weird sentence gets generated.
  If you encounter any issues, please let me know @identityarchitect on Tumblr or on the Adamantine's Drainbox thread of the <a href="https://yongasabi.freeforums.net/">Yongasabi Forums</a>.
</p>

<p><a href="https://perchance.org/yongasabi-generators-index">Yongasabi Generators Index</a></p>

